Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_aocv_analysis_mode(25.10)              timing_aocv_analysis_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_aocv_analysis_mode

Syntax
        timing_aocv_analysis_mode

       {launch_capture    |    clock_only   |   separate_data_clock   |   com-
       bine_launch_capture}

       Default: launch_capture

       Controls handling of AOCV analysis modes.

       When set to launch_capture, AOCV analysis will be  performed  for  both
       data  and  clock paths, and the AOCV derating factor will be calculated
       based on both clock and data path stages.

       When set to clock_only, AOCV analysis will be performed for clock paths
       only, and the AOCV derating factor will  be  calculated  based  on  the
       clock path stage depth only.

       When set to separate_data_clock, the software calculates the AOCV stage
       count  for  clock  paths and data paths separately. Both clock and data
       paths have related AOCV derating factors.

       When set to combine_launch_capture, the software calculates AOCV  stage
       count  using  combined  depth  for  launch  and  capture paths. This is
       achieved by summation of path depth on the launch and capture paths.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

